♪ Good-bye, gray sky,
hello, blue ♪

25:06.420 --> 25:08.920
♪ There's nothing can hold me
when I hold you ♪

25:09.420 --> 25:11.430
♪ It feels so right,
it can't be wrong ♪

25:11.840 --> 25:14.430
♪ Rockin' and rollin'
all week long ♪

